                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00H87/25.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Collector <persName type="from">Cobb</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">El Paso</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-06-30">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 30, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Trial Huerta and others postponed until July 12. When Huerta left Federal
                    building there was repetition of scene of June 27; he was given an ovation by
                    his partisans who are assembled in El Paso.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Cobb.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
